    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Layer Dependencies
    %% =====================================================

    Console --> Gateway
    REST --> Gateway
    WS --> Gateway
    CLI --> Gateway

    Gateway --> Deploy
    Gateway --> Workflow
    Gateway --> Policy
    Gateway --> Scheduler
    Gateway --> Plugin
    Gateway --> Secret

    Deploy --> Events
    Workflow --> Events
    Policy --> Events
    Scheduler --> Events
    Plugin --> Events
    Secret --> Events

    Deploy --> Metadata
    Workflow --> Metadata
    Policy --> Metadata

    Deploy --> Config
    Workflow --> Config

    Events --> Audit
    Events --> Observability
    Events --> Cache

    Events --> Relay
    Relay --> Protocol
    Protocol <-->|Persistent TLS| Agent

    Agent --> RuntimeMgr
    Agent --> Executor
    Agent --> Inventory
    Agent --> Health

    RuntimeMgr --> Containers
    RuntimeMgr --> Kubernetes
    RuntimeMgr --> VM
    RuntimeMgr --> WASM
    RuntimeMgr --> BareMetal

    Executor --> RuntimeMgr

    Inventory --> Observability
    Health --> Observability

    %% =====================================================
    %% Layer Rules
    %% =====================================================

    Rule1["Only communicates with adjacent layers"]
    Rule2["Higher layers never bypass lower layers"]

    Rule1 -.-> L4
    Rule2 -.-> L4

